start server on PORT 80 [RAILS]					- rvmsudo rails server -p 80
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
start server on PORT 80 using 'forever' [NODE.JS]		- sudo forever start index.js
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
list running processes controlled by 'forever'			- sudo forever list
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
stop running processes controlled by 'forever' 			- sudo forever stop <id in first column shown by list>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
run script with environment loaded 				- rails runner lib/<script_name>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
kill server 							- ps aux | grep node
								  kill -9 <pid of CHILD process>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
running background script					- nohup <> &
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
